### ============================================================
### EXPLORE API - REST Client Testing
### ============================================================
### Base URL — sesuaikan jika port berbeda
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api

### ============================================================
### PRASYARAT DATA DUMMY
### Jalankan sekali jika belum ada data explore:
### php artisan migrate
### php artisan db:seed
### ============================================================

### ============================================================
### 1. LIST LOWONGAN EXPLORE (default)
### Endpoint: GET /api/public/explore/jobs
### ============================================================

# @name exploreListDefault
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/explore/jobs
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================================
### 2. LIST LOWONGAN - PAGINATION
### Endpoint: GET /api/public/explore/jobs?page=1&per_page=6
### ============================================================

# @name exploreListPagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/explore/jobs?page=1&per_page=6
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================================
### 3. SEARCH - by posisi
### Endpoint: GET /api/public/explore/jobs?q=accounting
### ============================================================

# @name exploreSearchPosition
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/explore/jobs?q=accounting
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================================
### 4. SEARCH - by skill
### Endpoint: GET /api/public/explore/jobs?q=myob
### ============================================================

# @name exploreSearchSkill
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/explore/jobs?q=myob
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================================
### 5. SEARCH - by nama mitra (perusahaan/umkm)
### Endpoint: GET /api/public/explore/jobs?q=binajasa
### ============================================================

# @name exploreSearchMitra
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/explore/jobs?q=binajasa
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================================
### 6. FILTER - tipe pekerjaan + kebijakan kerja + lokasi + pengalaman + updated
### Endpoint:
### GET /api/public/explore/jobs?job_types[]=penuh_waktu&work_policies[]=kantor&provinces[]=DKI%20Jakarta&experience_levels[]=kurang_dari_setahun&updated_within=7d
### ============================================================

# @name exploreFilterCombined
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/explore/jobs?job_types[]=penuh_waktu&work_policies[]=kantor&provinces[]=DKI%20Jakarta&experience_levels[]=kurang_dari_setahun&updated_within=7d
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================================
### 7. FILTER - multiple job type sekaligus
### Endpoint: GET /api/public/explore/jobs?job_types[]=freelance&job_types[]=magang
### ============================================================

# @name exploreFilterMultiJobType
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/explore/jobs?job_types[]=freelance&job_types[]=magang
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================================
### 8. FILTER - format comma separated (didukung)
### Endpoint: GET /api/public/explore/jobs?job_types=freelance,magang
### ============================================================

# @name exploreFilterCommaSeparated
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/explore/jobs?job_types=freelance,magang
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================================
### 9. AMBIL DETAIL LOWONGAN
### Endpoint: GET /api/public/explore/jobs/{slug}
### Cara pakai:
### - Jalankan exploreListDefault dulu
### - Copy slug dari response data[0].slug
### - Ganti placeholder SLUG_DI_SINI
### ============================================================

# @name exploreDetail
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/explore/jobs/accounting-staff-1602be
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================================
### 10. DETAIL LOWONGAN - contoh not found (404)
### Endpoint: GET /api/public/explore/jobs/slug-tidak-ada
### ============================================================

# @name exploreDetailNotFound
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/explore/jobs/slug-tidak-ada
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================================
### 11. OPSI FILTER EXPLORE
### Endpoint: GET /api/public/explore/filters
### ============================================================

# @name exploreFilters
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/explore/filters
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================================
### 12. VALIDASI - updated_within tidak valid (422)
### Endpoint: GET /api/public/explore/jobs?updated_within=invalid
### ============================================================

# @name exploreInvalidUpdatedWithin
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/explore/jobs?updated_within=invalid
Accept: application/json

###
